Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------title------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:56.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,500)\pos(514,240)}虎與龍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.06,0:25:06.05,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,270)\fs35}龍兒與大河
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------正文------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上的任何人都有沒見過的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}輕鬆  漂亮  而柔和的表情  將她的心  輕輕地抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是騙人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}霉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊  不是發霉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前不久才除過霉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很溫柔非常甜美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}抹布  抹布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概  如果可以看見的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都會想要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界才把它藏了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓人無法那麼輕易地得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:00:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  弄不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}哼  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}只要有高須棒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總有一天會有人找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該得到的那個唯一的人  一定能把它找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣  產生了羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生態生態生態  生態平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龍  好冷淡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要上學  昨晚不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開學典禮啊  恭喜你升級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是對待迎接新學年的兒子的態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間好黑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙把窗簾拉開來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經拉開了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的公寓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼樣的傢伙住著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個建成之後  陽光的恩惠被奪去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得換洗的衣服都很難干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天每天  發霉發霉發霉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這敏銳眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龍越來越像你爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越像了  越來越像了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我和那人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加跟你爸爸一模一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龍已經要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的早飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在老地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕對不想被那麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你所稱讚的這個眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高高  高須同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下這個饒了我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就只有這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個應該可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  那就是殺人之眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}失物寄放  大橋高校雜務處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你  你真的總是撿到錢包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  還在同一個班就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了是同班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了  又…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年又是同班了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高須
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本年度的開學典禮到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回到各自的教室  做好班會的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的班級
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又得從解除大家的誤會開始才行麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不是所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有像這樣理解我的人在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在這個班裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  北村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也是同班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  櫛枝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是C班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高須同學是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像經常在北村同學周圍碰到你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛  櫛枝實乃梨對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然記得我的全名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我們一起清爽開朗地享受青春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  那個就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了高須
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍  稍微去一下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就顛峰對決了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人和逢阪大河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就開始決賽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新舊老大爭奪戰麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像人偶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺微妙地給人以威懾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一不小心就會被吃掉一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良高須和掌中老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}註：「大河」與「老虎」日文發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,30)\fs22}像老虎一樣兇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(520,30)\fs22}但是很小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌中老虎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌中老…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名副其實…不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼今天就到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有交志願調查表的同學等會兒到辦公室來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好嗎  高須同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的時候也遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為鼻炎去看了醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是因為室內灰塵什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  現代病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌中老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙和櫛枝實乃梨是朋友麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭受慘狀的明明是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  逢阪同學和高須同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然掌中老虎很強大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是高須同學只是外表可怕而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤會好像很快就解開了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高  高須同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是對自己的前途有些迷惘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但但  但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志願調查表除了你以外大家都交了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該說你是對自己的前途迷茫的單親不良學生對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣不知深淺…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限時銷售要結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書包書包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之放著別管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你在幹什麼什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我只是拿書包…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是你的書包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的座位是那旁邊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難  難道說列…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列列列…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列…列弄錯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼搶我的書包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  適可而止…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢阪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢  在天國裏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好帥的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是為了不用擔心被刺殺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在肚皮上放著一本週刊雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被電到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為跟你相像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說可是個大麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是長著這張臉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就不會怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會被掌中老虎纏上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該對自己更有自信才對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志願調查表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北村祐作大人收
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢阪…大河
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  放錯地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面的東西沒看過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也完全想不出是什麼內容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  還給你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重新粘回去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常笨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  泰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還不到回來的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  讓我們繼續喝下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}高須泰子  花名-未羅乃  工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的  小未羅乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  這個尺寸…好像在哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢阪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我用面紙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什  什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼給我忘掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那封…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西既然被你知道了  我就已經沒臉活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一死了之了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼要殺的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想死  所以只好把你殺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然  就把記憶全部抹除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  只要用這個用力敲打腦門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不會斷氣  至少可以讓記憶消失得一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我聽好了  那封信…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看過了吧  讀過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所  所以說那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  那封情…情書的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空…的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  所以別說內容了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒應該說還沒交給北村真是太幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒暴出這樣的失態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底餓到什麼程度了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便利店已經吃膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便利店？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你父母不給你做…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家家都有一本難念的經吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時要是乖乖把書包給我就不會這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要怎麼給我善後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉上還粘著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你這種為了讓炒飯的油染上大蒜味的而出生的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情…情書哪裏丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  那可不是值得羞恥的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是什麼你明白嗎  你不會明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1}那個是以「如果我要為喜歡的女孩子舉行演唱會」為主題而做的列表
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了她而即興作的詩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她一起出去兜風時聽的MD  當然沒有駕照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面還根據春夏秋冬不同季節有四種主題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  噁心死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有告白的勇氣  所以只有這樣妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這的確很沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不覺得這是羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你可以拿出自信來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是只在那裏妄想  而是已經打算付諸於行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得更積極一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清爽地  開朗地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「獻給櫛枝實乃梨小姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  就像櫛枝實乃梨一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然對實乃梨…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦  你也沒資格說別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  不是讓你忘掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉  囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷  冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  小鸚  吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我看什麼啊  真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼  對我家重要的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！  很好  小鸚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快向客人做自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天終於說出自己的名字了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸚…鵡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  今天的小鸚不在狀態上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已經這個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們是一丘之貉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事不會和任何人說的  相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說你都吃過飯了  快給我回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  請你快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那某種意義上「有病」的媽媽要回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  要  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…吶  情書到底怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不流行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼在這種時候扭扭捏捏的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛咨詢的話以後隨時都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已經不早了明天再說  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？你願意幫助我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做  我做我做我做  什麼都做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會像狗一樣的忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我什麼都聽從？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做  我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就這樣吧  好嗎  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙怎麼從窗戶進來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  反正很近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也帶著木刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那樣才是危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  那個洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種程度隨便找點紙糊上去就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話就用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要花錢的話  之後我會付的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見了  龍兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是不是直接叫了我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是高…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來  你不是發誓…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你掛斷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來是去哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽台上  為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你答應過會像狗一樣什麼都做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那個是指關於你和北村的事我會幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來的話會怎麼樣你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就讓你明白也行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等我十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜燴飯還有十分鐘就煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真強大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門…門開著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢…逢阪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好特別的氣味…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢阪！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢阪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢阪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢阪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我  請務必讓我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃這裏的廚房！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  回籠覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像做出來的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著的逢阪真的就像一個人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有生活感的這間屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是過家家用的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  作為人偶的屋子尺寸也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有十五分左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還在打掃中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致已經乾淨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠嗆的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水槽的積水都發臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排水溝裏全是粘液黴菌和發臭的垃圾  簡直就是地獄繪圖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間裏也到處都是灰塵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不法侵入  而且還強制打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.77,0:22:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有自覺啊  你這條狗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.22,0:22:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣說對狗太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.29,0:22:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣是狗你也是劣等狗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劣  等  狗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.95,0:22:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等不知感恩的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家特地…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  「我開動了」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大米之神  各位生產者  我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來不流鼻涕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為變乾淨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.54,0:24:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂七八糟的協定  產生的誤解  遺傳因子的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.08,0:25:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河  你真是個讓人感到佩服的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.49,0:25:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  然後給我爛掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------OPED------
